
STEP 1: Fill this JSON template.

STEP 2: Open the second tab (automatically opened) and upload your preview image.

STEP 3: Copy the RAW image link from GitHub.

STEP 4: Replace "PASTE_RAW_IMAGE_LINK_HERE" with the actual image link.

--------------------------------------------------

Create a new JSON file inside the /submissions folder.

Example file name:
my-awesome-block.json

Use this format:

{
  "id": "unique-id",
  "title": "Your block title",
  "description": "Short description",
  "category": "Buttons / Navbar / Cards / Layout",
  "language": "HTML / CSS / JS / React",
  "tags": ["tag1", "tag2"],
  "preview": "PASTE_RAW_IMAGE_LINK_HERE",
  "code": "PASTE YOUR CODE HERE",
  "author": "your-github-username"
}

Then commit & create a Pull Request.
